	METHOD b zoom (F)V
		COMMENT Values greater than 1 zoom out, values less than 1 zoom in.
		COMMENT Multiplicative, i.e. repeated calls to this method will have a stacking effect,
		COMMENT meaning that the zoom factor is a factor and not something absolute.
		COMMENT
		COMMENT Does not zoom arbitrarily far out after a certain point, see {@link #getDesiredZoom()}.
		ARG 0 zoomFactor
